thing that can happen.

52:50.000 --> 52:52.036 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And, hopefully,
the reader will want to come
along, right?

52:52.036 --> 52:52.703 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JOHN IRVING: Yes. Yes. Yes.

52:52.703 --> 52:53.604 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

52:53.604 --> 52:56.407 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: The novel
is "Avenue of Mysteries."

52:56.407 --> 52:57.174 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
John Irving, thanks so much.

52:57.174 --> 53:02.446 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
